{"tid":2435554,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李家超：總之共產黨話咩我跟住做就係啦","createTime":"2021-03-06T10:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T12:37:13.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f14ef8a3da2de101d51580c358aa7b5f9f289a68","tid":2435554,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T10:21:28.000Z","msg":"李家超撰文支持中央修改香港選舉制度 保安局將全力配合<br />\n<br />\n保安局長李家超發表文章，表示全面支持中央對完善選舉制度的決定，指保安局會全力配合，繼續無畏無懼，履行維護國家根本利益和香港繁榮穩定的使命。<br />\n<br />\n李家超說，雖然在《香港國安法》實施後，香港漸漸回復穩定，但選舉制度的漏洞和缺陷繼續存在，對香港社會穩定及國家的安全構成直接隱憂，問題必須徹底解決，方可確保「一國兩制」行穩致遠，香港特區長治久安。他說「愛國者治港」，天經地義，理所當然，反問有何國家會接受叛國者管治，由分裂國家、顛覆國家主權或要求外國干預內部事務、損害國家和市民利益的人管治。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381866\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2381866&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=73ae965c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381866</a>"},{"pid":"d17ee9aff2f6cd52b7a3324c1d741d0c2ff37cc6","tid":2435554,"uid":95577,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T10:25:27.000Z","msg":"全力配合喺咪即係一有人反對<br />\n就搵黑警打柒佢<br />\n好似跑馬地果單咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27b72ab563e4b3e794893917fb2ad4a2df2c7bf","tid":2435554,"uid":117689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T10:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363cd647b21bd28a5056242c6e383378189061c5","tid":2435554,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d27b72ab563e4b3e794893917fb2ad4a2df2c7bf","tid":2435554,"uid":117689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T10:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T10:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58548936e7d1463bebca9096d60c50